President Trump is requesting an expedited investigation of justice for George Floyd’s fatal arrest. According to a couple of tweets, Trump said that the FBI and the Department of Justice are already well into the investigation at his request. George Floyd: Police fire pepper spray on protesters during demonstration over killing of Black man in U.S. At my request, the FBI and the Department of Justice are already well into an investigation as to the very sad and tragic death in Minnesota of George Floyd…. ….I have asked for this investigation to be expedited and greatly appreciate all of the work done by local law enforcement. My heart goes out to George’s family and friends. Justice will be served!